- Offering 3 Sheep and 2 Wheat (total value: 3*13 + 2*6 = 39 + 12 = 51)
- Requesting 3 Brick (total value: 3*23 = 69)
- Net gain: 69 - 51 = 18 value

This leverages my surplus Sheep and Wheat while acquiring higher-value Brick. I have enough resources to make this offer without risking scarcity.

[Offer: 3 Sheep, 2 Wheat -> 3 Brick]
